<HEADLINE>
FT  21 JUN 94 / People: Non-executive directors
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
David Bucks, former deputy chairman of Hill Samuel Bank, and John Morgan,
ex-chief executive of Imro, at YAMAICHI BANK.
</TEXT>
<XX>
