FT  21 JUN 94 / Bectu calls off strike threat
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Bectu, the main technical union at the BBC, yesterday called off the threat
of immediate further industrial action and decided to enter up to eight
weeks of detailed talks with the management.
